<font color="#FF0000">A HEALING PLACE</font><br>
<tt>Tue Apr 29 12:58:10 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
It was 12 years after the dedication before I could bring myself to visit the WALL. I spite of my minimal participation by being at sea on a carrier, the WALL hit me like a hammer. My wife and I visited together. I really needed her support. I pledge to live my life, so that theirs was not sacrificed in vain.<br>
It is a beautiful, sacred place. A healing place.<br>

